Show HN: Manage research papers from your CLI
text:
I built this because I started reading a lot of arXiv papers and wanted a quick way to store and download them.

Features:

- Add a bunch of arXiv papers to Notion with auto-populated title/URL/date/authors in one command

- Download PDFs of any papers you haven't saved yet in one command
